rComments: This is the most difficult class I've ever taken, but the most enjoyable. The information was incredibly interesting, and Dr. Johnson presented things not in any of the textbooks--it was notes custom made for the course.
Overall, I liked the guy. I like his grading scale. He can be a little boring, but overall he's a pretty decent teacher and dude.
Nobody wants to take theory but he makes it a fun class...Sometimes you're not really sure what he's saying though. He's truly a hippie at heart.
